    "english": "ZIYARAH OF IMAM ZAYN AL ABIDIN, IMAM MUHAMMAD AL BAQIR & IMAM JAFAR AL SADIQ (A) ON TUESDAY\r\n\r\nThis day is dedicated to the Imams Ali ibn al-Husayn Zayn al-’Abidin, Muhammad ibn Ali al-Baqir, and Ja’far ibn Muhammad al-Sadiq - peace be upon them all. Their Ziyarah on Tuesdays is as follows:\r\n\r\nPeace be on you, O depositories of Allah’s knowledge! Peace be on you, O interpreters of Allah’s Revelation! Peace be on you, O leaders to true guidance! Peace be on you, O signs of piety! Peace be on you, O descendants of Allah’s Messenger! I recognize your rights, I discernibly acknowledge your true standing, I incur the hostility of your enemies, and I show loyalty to your loyalists. May Allah accept me, my father, and mother as ransoms for you! Blessings of Allah be upon you. O Allah, I am willingly showing loyalty to the last of them just as I have shown loyalty to the first of them, I release myself from any confidant other than them, and I reject all idols, false deities, al-Lat, and al-'Uzza. Blessings of Allah be upon you, O my Masters! Mercy of Allah and His benedictions be upon you, too. Peace be upon you, O master of the worshippers and descendant of the Prophets’ successors. Peace be upon you, O he who split open the knowledge of the Prophets. Peace be upon you, O veracious and honest in all [your] words and deeds. O my Masters! Today is your day, which is Tuesday, and on this day, I am your guest and I am in your vicinity; so, receive me as your guest and treat me as your neighbor, [I ask you] by Allah’s standing with you and with your Household, the pure and immaculate. "
